WEBVTT

00:03:59.587 --> 00:04:04.113
For example, how does
a fascist evaluate art?

00:04:04.615 --> 00:04:09.904
How does a fascist decide whether a movie
is a good movie or a bad movie?

00:04:10.728 --> 00:04:14.900
Well, it's very, very, very simple.

00:04:15.260 --> 00:04:17.188
There is really just one yardstick:

00:04:17.593 --> 00:04:21.069
if the movie serves
the interests of the nation,

00:04:21.093 --> 00:04:22.537
it's a good movie;

00:04:22.561 --> 00:04:25.744
if the movie doesn't serve
the interests of the nation,

00:04:25.768 --> 00:04:26.990
it's a bad movie.

00:04:27.014 --> 00:04:28.164
That's it.

00:04:28.496 --> 00:04:33.384
Similarly, how does a fascist decide
what to teach kids in school?